    ClearGraph

    public class DropGraph
extends AbstractOneGraphManagement
    The DROP operation removes the specified graph(s) from the Graph Store. 
     DROP  ( SILENT )? (GRAPH IRIref | DEFAULT | NAMED | ALL | GRAPHS | SOLUTIONS | SOLUTIONS %VARNAME)
    Note: Bigdata does not support empty graphs, so DROP and CLEAR have identical semantics.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
    See Also:
    http://www.w3.org/TR/sparql11-update/#drop, Serialized Form
